HEADWORD: Candleholder
<hw>Can"dle*hold`er</hw> <pr>(#)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who, or
that which, holds a candle; also, one who assists another, but is
otherwise not of importance.</def> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

